OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fheavy showers will gradually die out
OL,7,Fthis evening, leaving the rest of the
OL,8,Fnight largely dry with a few clear
OL,9,Fspells developing. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA mainly dry, bright
OL,12,Fmorning, perhaps the odd light shower.
OL,13,FTurning overcast through the afternoon
OL,14,Fas rain spreads in from the west
OL,15,Flater, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
