OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright and breezy on Thursday with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and a few
OL,8,Fshowers. Risk of patchy rain in west
OL,9,Fon Friday and Saturday, mainly dry and
OL,10,Fbright in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
